<div style="text-align:center">

    <div class="jumbotron">
        <div class="container">
          <h1>Empowering Project-Based-Learning <small><br>K-12 STEM Project Kits for Teachers</small></h1>
        </div>
    </div>

    <div class="container">
       <div class="row">
            <div class="col-md-6">
                <h2><strong>What's a kit?</strong></h2>
                <h3>Highly affordable<br><small>$1-10 per student per kit</small></h3>
                <h3>Standards-integrated<br><small>NGSS, Common Core, and ISTE</small></h3>
                <h3>Completely pre-packaged<br><small>Lesson plans and materials: everything you need!</small></h3>
            </div>
           <div class="col-md-1"></div> 
           <div class="col-md-4">
                <h2><strong>Submit a project!</strong></h2>
                <h3>You know that INCREDIBLE activity you created to teach that thing you love? 
                    Submit it to the platform and get paid a cut of sales.<br>
                    <small>Subject to a painless submission process, of course.</small>
                    <br> Coming soon!
                </h3>
            <div class="col-md-1"></div>    
            </div>

        </div>
    </div>

    <div class="jumbotron">
        <div class="container">
            <h1>Get Explorious <small><br>Pick a subject below! </small></h1>
        </div>
    </div>

    <section class="no-padding" id="portfolio">
        <div class="container-fluid">
            <div class="row no-gutter popup-gallery">
                <% @subjects.each do |subject| %>
                    <div class="col-lg-4 col-sm-6">
                        <%=link_to projects_path(:subject => subject.id), :class => 'portfolio-box' do %>
                            <img src=<%=subject.image%> class="img-responsive" alt="">
                            <div class="ghost-title" style = "background: <%= subject.color %>;"> 
                                <%= subject.name %> 
                            </div>
                            <div class="portfolio-box-caption" style = "background: <%= subject.color %>"> 
                                <div class="portfolio-box-caption-content" >
                                    <div class="project-category text-faded">
                                        <%=subject.name%>
                                    </div>
                                    <div class="project-name">
                                        Explore Curriculum-Integrated Projects
                                    </div>
                                </div>
                            </div>
                        <% end %>
                    </div>
                <% end %>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>

    <div class="jumbotron">
        <div class="container">
            <h1>How about us? <small><br>Here's why we do this</small></h1>
        </div>
    </div>

    <div class="container">
        <div clas="row">
            <div class="col-md-1"></div>
            <div class="col-md-10">
                <h3>We believe we can broadly increase the quality and equity of high quality STEM education by empowering teachers to spend less time and money preparing projects. We're very much a work in progress and we would love to hear from you!</h3>
                
                (Render form)
            </div>
            <div class="col-md-1"></div>
        </div>
    </div>

</div>